lines.words: Why can't I talk about it?
I don't even know what to say to you.
(you)
All the nights I try to act.
I don't understand my lack, of control.
Sorry baby I can figure this out.
Maybe I should just shut my mouth.
In and out I'm drifting,
underneath the clouds.
Sorry baby, can you figure me out?
Psilocybin blur - I get around.
In and out I drift. You kiss me [as I'm]
floating back down.
Crop circles carved in my chest.
The vines all wrap up the mess.
I drive around in my head,
back where I began
It's all these stupid games that I play

Cause I don't wanna show you 
 how the scars won't fade away.
[Outro]
